metadata.name: UNMASKING #1
metadata.description:
Can ‘revealing a true nature’ provoke feelings of shame, embarrassment, and judgment? Or is it about desire and human instincts? Creating via provocation is another form of art that invites a viewer to observe their own emotions and depict how it makes them feel.

Part of the UNMASKING collection was created in the streets of central Helsinki, where photographers and a model witnessed exaggerated emotional reactions of passers-by. Can a female nude body cause society to glitch?
